textfsm_template:
Value FEX_ID (\d+)
Value DESCRIPTION (\S+)
Value STATE (\S+)
Value FEX_VERSION (\S+)
Value SWITCH_VERSION (\S+)
Value SWITCHPORTS (.+)
Value FABRIC_PORTS (.+)

Start
  ^FEX:\s+${FEX_ID}
  ^\s+Description:\s+${DESCRIPTION}
  ^\s+State:\s+${STATE}
  ^\s+FEX version:\s+${FEX_VERSION}\s+\[Switch version:\s+${SWITCH_VERSION}\]
  ^\s+Switchport\[s\]:\s+${SWITCHPORTS}
  ^\s+Fabric port\[s\]:\s+${FABRIC_PORTS} -> Record
